================================================================================
                           数据库实体关系
================================================================================

  User (用户)
    |
    +-- documents: Document[] (创建/拥有的文档)
    +-- comments: Comment[] (发布的评论)
    +-- projects: Project[] (参与的项目)
    +-- spaces: Space[] (管理的空间)
    +-- meetings: Meeting[] (创建的会议)

  Document (文档)
    |
    +-- blocks: Block[] (文档块)
    +-- comments: Comment[] (文档评论)
    +-- annotations: Annotation[] (批注)
    +-- versions: Version[] (版本历史)
    +-- owner: User (所有者)

  Project (项目)
    |
    +-- tasks: Task[] (任务列表)
    +-- owner: User (创建者)
    +-- members: User[] (成员)

  Space (空间)
    |
    +-- bases: KnowledgeBase[] (知识库)
    +-- owner: User (所有者)
    +-- members: User[] (成员)

  KnowledgeBase (知识库)
    |
    +-- nodes: KnowledgeNode[] (文档节点)
    +-- space: Space (所属空间)

================================================================================
                           WebSocket 实时协作架构
================================================================================

  Documents Gateway (WebSocket)
  |
  +-- Room Management
  |    +-- joinRoom(documentId, userId)
  |    +-- leaveRoom(documentId, userId)
  |
  +-- Event Handlers
  |    +-- onBlockUpdate: 块更新
  |    +-- onBlockDelete: 块删除
  |    +-- onBlockAdd: 新增块
  |    +-- onCursorMove: 光标移动
  |    +-- onSelectionChange: 选区变化
  |    +-- onChatMessage: 聊天消息
  |
  +-- Collaboration Features
  |    +-- Operational Transform (操作转换)
  |    +-- Block Locking (块锁)
  |    +-- Presence (在线状态)

================================================================================
                           API 端点总览
================================================================================

  认证 (Auth)
    POST /auth/login - 用户登录 (每日动态邀请码)

  文档 (Documents)
    GET    /documents          - 获取文档列表
    GET    /documents/:id     - 获取单个文档
    POST   /documents         - 创建文档
    GET    /documents/tree     - 获取文档树
    POST   /documents/:id/toggle-star - 收藏
    POST   /documents/:id/trash       - 移至回收站
    POST   /documents/:id/restore    - 恢复
    DELETE /documents/:id            - 永久删除
    POST   /documents/:id/analyze    - 智能分析

  批注评论 (Comments)
    GET    /documents/:id/comments      - 获取评论
    POST   /documents/:id/comments      - 添加评论
    PUT    /comments/:id               - 更新评论
    DELETE /comments/:id               - 删除评论
    POST   /comments/:id/reply         - 回复
    POST   /comments/:id/react         - 反应

  批注 (Annotations)
    GET    /documents/:id/annotations   - 获取批注
    POST   /documents/:id/annotations   - 创建批注
    PUT    /annotations/:id             - 更新批注
    DELETE /annotations/:id             - 删除批注
    POST   /annotations/:id/resolve     - 解决批注

  项目 (Projects)
    GET    /projects             - 获取项目列表
    POST   /projects            - 创建项目
    GET    /projects/:id        - 获取项目详情
    PUT    /projects/:id        - 更新项目
    DELETE /projects/:id        - 删除项目
    GET    /projects/:id/tasks  - 获取任务
    POST   /projects/:id/tasks  - 创建任务
    PUT    /tasks/:id           - 更新任务
    DELETE /tasks/:id           - 删除任务

  知识库 (Knowledge)
    GET    /knowledge/spaces           - 获取空间列表
    POST   /knowledge/spaces           - 创建空间
    GET    /knowledge/spaces/:id/bases - 获取知识库
    POST   /knowledge/spaces/:id/bases - 创建知识库
    GET    /knowledge/bases/:id/tree  - 获取目录树

  会议 (Meetings)
    GET    /meetings         - 获取会议列表
    POST   /meetings        - 创建会议
    GET    /meetings/:id    - 获取会议详情
    POST   /meetings/:id/join  - 加入会议
    POST   /meetings/:id/leave - 离开会议
    GET    /meetings/:id/token  - 获取令牌

================================================================================
